test.name: System.Buffers.Text.Tests.Base64UrlDecoderUnitTests.BasicDecodingWithExtraWhitespaceShouldBeCountedInConsumedBytes(inputString: \"M TIzM TIzM TIzM TIz\", expectedConsumed: 20, expectedWritten: 12)
System.Buffers.Text.Tests.Base64UrlDecoderUnitTests.BasicDecodingWithExtraWhitespaceShouldBeCountedInConsumedBytes(inputString: \"MT IzMT IzMT IzMT Iz\", expectedConsumed: 20, expectedWritten: 12)
System.Buffers.Text.Tests.Base64UrlDecoderUnitTests.BasicDecodingWithExtraWhitespaceShouldBeCountedInConsumedBytes(inputString: \"MTI zMTI zMTI zMTI z\", expectedConsumed: 20, expectedWritten: 12)

System.Buffers.Text.Tests.Base64UrlDecoderUnitTests.BasicDecodingWithExtraWhitespaceShouldBeCountedInConsumedBytes(inputString: \"M TI zM TI zM TI zM TI z\", expectedConsumed: 44, expectedWritten: 12)

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<LOW>\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 1, expectedOperationStatus: DestinationTooSmall, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<LOW>\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 2, expectedOperationStatus: Done, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 1, expectedOperationStatus: DestinationTooSmall, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 2, expectedOperationStatus: Done, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>\", isFinalChunk: False, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 1, expectedOperationStatus: NeedMoreData, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>X\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 2, expectedOperationStatus: DestinationTooSmall, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>X\", isFinalChunk: False, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 2, expectedOperationStatus: DestinationTooSmall, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>X\", isFinalChunk: True, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 3, expectedOperationStatus: Done, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD58\")

System.Text.Unicode.Tests.Utf8Tests.ToBytes_WithReplacements_AndCustomBufferSizes(utf16Input: \"é<HIGH>X\", isFinalChunk: False, expectedNumCharsConsumed: 3, expectedOperationStatus: Done, expectedUtf8TranscodingHex: \"C3A9EFBFBD58\")
